readability_reflection: Concatenation because I have worked with concatenation before, although brief. I have never worked with interpolation but it still felt harder to read.
comprehension_debugging: Interpolation has challenges. You really have to train your mind to deal with the addition symbol.
preference_rationale: I would prefer concatenation based on experience with it.
learning_curve: It eased my mind because it felt familiar.
suggestions_improvement: Maybe an added symbol to know exactly which part is going to be added.
